g.title: j3752759978
g.text: u spend a lot of time in that backroom.

g.title: j1773382278
g.text: how is my roguish perfectionist today?

g.title: j1198411402
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j3961988752
g.text: Thanks for checking in. I'm doing fine.

g.title: j1353498438
g.text: our mysterious hero from the future! u doing well?

g.title: j804225340
g.text: how are u today? not being too hard on urself, I hope

g.title: j1891683032
g.text: how is my fave time traveler?

g.title: j1703075487
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j3152438637
g.text: Cute. Lol. Okay, I admit it. I've had better days.

g.title: j2774212699
g.text: I don't think pinky swears work online.

g.title: j1629165716
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j3841668538
g.text: then swear on something important to u!

g.title: j1124515088
g.text: good I just wanted to make sure <3

g.title: j622849329
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j3777810110
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j3467505280
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j3630901114
g.text: anything I can do to make ur day better?

g.title: j2730475618
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j4272193604
g.text: You could tell me a joke.

g.title: j23194351
g.text: Pretty lady like you? I can think of a few things. ;)

g.title: j3387003320
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j469537665
g.text: Okay, I confess. I've had better days.

g.title: j3110885608
g.text: Can't you just accept I'm fine?

g.title: j377657138
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j2980474055
g.text: a suspiciously curt answer but ok

g.title: j651088760
g.text: med pack ur bags. we're going to the future!

g.title: j3218085200
g.text: hope u don't mind me getting a bit serious for a sec

g.title: j3598827982
g.text: I see u pushing yourself for others without ever asking for anything in return

g.title: j67044345
g.text: so I just wanna say, if u ever want to share some those burdens u carry, I'm always here

g.title: j3212908573
g.text: I appreciate you saying that, Aoi. I'll keep it in mind.

g.title: j827502003
g.text: You should deal with your own issues before trying to take on someone else's.

g.title: j174130761
g.text: I bet you say that to everyone.

g.title: j2344071879
g.text: I don't think we can help ourselves without helping others too

g.title: j2135506731
g.text: only the people I care about

g.title: j1429107748
g.text: ^_^ ok enough serious talk for now

g.title: j273356512
g.text: but that's a topic for another time

g.title: j1026134735
g.text: may the rest of ur day be lovely
